com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.processor

Class STCustomModelAdaptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.stringtemplate.v4.misc.ObjectModelAdaptor
      • com.fortyoneconcepts.valjogen.processor.STCustomModelAdaptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.stringtemplate.v4.ModelAdaptor

    public class STCustomModelAdaptor
extends org.stringtemplate.v4.misc.ObjectModelAdaptor
    ST model adapter that handles normal ST properies AND do the following magic conversions: Type.exactType_xxx -> Type.isExactType(java.lang.String), with argument consisting og xxx with underscores replaced by dot. Type.ofType_xxx -> Type.isOfType(java.lang.String), with argument consisting og xxx with underscores replaced by dot. Type.instanceMethod_xxx -> Type.hasInstanceMethod(java.lang.String),with argument consisting of the overload name format of xxx (i.e. underscores replaced by dot + paranthesis). Type.staticMethod_xxx -> Type.hasStaticMethod(java.lang.String), with argument consisting of the overload name format of xxx (i.e. underscores replaced by dot + paranthesis). Type.instanceMember_xxx -> Type.hasInstanceMember(java.lang.String), where xxx is used as argument. Type.staticMember_xxx -> Type.hasStaticMember(java.lang.String), where xxx is used as argument.
